entries.s_10: Ohh, my hand! I burned it while repairing one of the X-95 starfighters in the hangar. Do you have anything for the pain?
entries.s_16: Thank you so much! My hand feels better now. I think I'll rest here for a while, though.
entries.s_17: I can help you. I have a bactapack.
